      <title>‘불수능’에 치열해진 정시… “대학별 영어 반영 방식 잘 살펴야”</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/education/2025/12/22/QAVHT4SS3NHZTJSLJQZJCVNO7Q/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/education/2025/12/22/QAVHT4SS3NHZTJSLJQZJCVNO7Q/</guid>
